> Hi neighbors,
>
> Hope you are all doing well. Some updates:
>
> *Join our meeting on Tuesday May 5, 7PM-8PM *(Every two weeks, for now)
>
>    - We'll be encouraging everyone to introduce themselves and discussing
>    upcoming actions. A meeting summary will be included in the Friday email.
> - *Join by Video Call:* To join the video call, click this link: https://
>    meet.google.com/zjf-ihai-msy <https://meet.google.com/zjf-ihai-msy> .
